Miss Parker's office.

462
00:25:11,510 --> 00:25:13,219
Hi, Katharine.

463
00:25:13,304 --> 00:25:14,429
You what?

464
00:25:14,805 --> 00:25:16,472
Broke it skiing.

465
00:25:16,557 --> 00:25:19,017
They can't move me
for weeks.

466
00:25:19,101 --> 00:25:20,643
This is what I need
you to do.

467
00:25:21,770 --> 00:25:23,938
Water plants, O.K.

468
00:25:25,608 --> 00:25:27,775
Cable comes on Friday,
right.

469
00:25:28,027 --> 00:25:30,111
Hey, easy with the leg.

470
00:25:30,237 --> 00:25:32,155
Quit staring up my gown.

471
00:25:32,573 --> 00:25:34,699
I'm staying
at my parents' house,

472
00:25:34,783 --> 00:25:36,701
and the housekeeper
is in Barbados for a month.

473
00:25:36,785 --> 00:25:38,661
Wouldn't you know it?
What a mess.

474
00:25:38,871 --> 00:25:40,371
You need to let in
the flower man

475
00:25:40,456 --> 00:25:42,290
and the cleaning lady.

476
00:25:42,374 --> 00:25:44,959
The entrance code
for the front door is...

477
00:25:46,462 --> 00:25:49,464
[Whispering]
It's 7-5-4-3-2000.

478
00:25:50,299 --> 00:25:53,176
I know there's more,
but I can't think of what.

479
00:25:53,260 --> 00:25:54,886
Go through
my desk calendar.

480
00:25:54,970 --> 00:25:57,472
There's a bunch of invitations
to be RSVP'd.

481
00:25:58,307 --> 00:26:01,392
I know I'm asking
an awful lot, Tess.

